text: Discover the pinnacle of luxury and sustainability in Bellingham! This 4-bed, 2.75-bath, 2218 sqft home on 6.31 acres offers eco-friendly living with a private well and 15, 000-gallon rain catchment system. The property includes a 3, 750 sqft shop with office and half bath, a 398 sqft tiny home, a 400 sqft stand alone bonus room, and solar panels for energy efficiency. Outdoor features include two ponds with fountain and waterfall, stocked with bass. Inside, enjoy an open floor plan with a stylish kitchen with quartz countertops, beautiful ceramic tile floors, separate dining room, and breakfast nook. Raised garden beds, covered RV parking, and a back patio with electric awning complete this dream home and more! No HOA or C C and R's!

Gorgeous like new home with peaceful mountain and valley views located on the outer ridge of the development. 4bd, 3.5bath + upper loft with skylights to bring that natural light. Great room and kitchen are perfect to entertain or just hang out, including a spacious dining area that extends from the kitchen. Quartz counter tops throughout the home and an oversized kitchen island with eating bar. Dual primary suites on the main floor with walk-in closets & custom tile showers. Large laundry room with sink, and plenty of cabinets for storage. Oversized covered outdoor living area perfect for entertaining. Home features a heat pump, vinyl plank floors and almost a 10, 000 sqft lot that backs up to the most beautiful surroundings. A must See!

The Lupine V2 by MainVue Homes at Horizon is an expansive design with sweeping views. The Signature Outdoor Room is uniquely located at the front of the home, providing an all-season escape to enjoy mountain and ocean views. The Gourmet Kitchen is flush with 3m Quartz counters, Stainless Steel appliances, and a Grand Butlers Pantry with access to the Garage. Enjoy the open-flow layout between the Great Room, Gourmet Kitchen, and Dining Room, plus an entertainment ready Multi-Purpose Room at the rear of the home. Upstairs, find the Grand Suite with a designer free-standing tub and 76 tall frameless glass walk-in shower, followed by the Leisure Room and secondary bedrooms.

Absolutely stunning and move-in ready, welcome to 380 E Pole Road #2 in beautiful Lynden! This home has been completely remodeled from floor to ceiling, featuring a new roof, new flooring, and fresh paint in modern colors. The updated and spacious kitchen, beautiful large bathrooms, and generously sized bedrooms offer comfort and styletoo much to mention! Located in the heart of Whatcom County at Royal Coachman Mobile Estates, a desirable 55+ community with some of the lowest space rents around. Dont miss out on this incredible opportunity! Schedule a showing today!

READY FOR SUMMER! Enjoy the custom and premium features of this lake cottage in a 14-acre resort setting. Imaginerelaxing and entertaining on the double upper deck with loved ones, enjoying the lake view by the fireplace and taking ashort walk to the beach, marina, and resort amenities. The largest cottage available, and most comfortable sleeping loftand master bedroom with slider to the green space. This high-quality custom-built cottage, fun community and awesome lake access makes for a hyper functional vacation lifestyle!

Welcome to Douglas Farm - a charming new home community in Ferndale - just 15 min from Bellingham! This beautiful Bedford plan offers smartly designed living spaces & high end features throughout. The main floor features an inviting great room w/cozy fireplace & gourmet kitchen w/massive island, 5 burner gas cooktop, walk-in pantry & adjacent sunroom plus a powder rm, pocket office & covered patio. Upstairs, you'll find a primary suite w/lavish bath, 2 secondary BRs, a spacious loft & utility rm. Extras include landscaping, irrigation, fencing, 9 ft ceilings, central heating/cooling, EV charger & more! If you are working w/a licensed broker, please register your broker on your 1st visit per our site reg policy. ASK ABOUT SPECIAL FINANCING!

New construction! Gorgeous location! This brand new 3 bed, 1.75 bath is located near gas, grocery, post office and coffee, in addition to all your favorite outdoor mountain adventures. Close to camping at Silver Lake Park, skiing and snowboarding during the winter and hiking adventures at nearby trailheads in warmer months. Unwind with a beautiful view of the foothills after a long day of excitement. The exterior insulation has been upgraded beyond the building code requirements for better home temperature efficiency and noise dampening. Additionally, the interior walls have been insulated for noise dampening between rooms. The house is a blank canvas waiting for you to make it home, an adventure getaway or a possible AirBnB!

Fall in love with PNW sunsets over Bellingham Bay! Floor to ceiling windows frame 180 degree views of downtown Bellingham and the waterfront, while sweeping natural light fills the main room. The expansive west facing deck is perfect for a morning reset or evenings entertaining friends with a million dollar backdrop. A perfectly updated kitchen with quartz countertops, gray shaker cabinets and stainless appliances give the unit a modern, elevated feel. Two generous sized bedrooms and a large bathroom with new vanity and quartz counters. Enjoy the convenience of one assigned covered parking space and close proximity to WWU, parks, and downtown Bellingham!

Unmatched character with modern updates in an amazing location just steps to downtown. Enjoy main level living with two large bedrooms on the main floor, easy access from your carport or perch up in the primary suite with views of downtown. Light flows through with 10 foot high ceilings, bay windows and gorgeous turn of the century columns. Expand into your entertaining space on a new, nearly 200 square foot Wolf Serenity deck or relax in your 6-person sauna. Walking distance to Nelson's Market, downtown, grocery stores and restaurants. Truly a special home and a must see!

Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom house. This property offers a range of features that are sure to impress. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by a covered front porch. The main floor features a versatile den/office space that could easily be converted into a 4th bedroom to suit your needs. The 2-car garage includes a convenient bump-out area, ideal for a workshop or additional storage. This home highlights a custom fireplace The rear-facing great room concept seamlessly connects the kitchen and dining room, creating an inviting space for entertaining. The kitchen boasts ample counter space, a walk-in pantry, an island, and a spacious dining area. Step outside onto the oversized back deck. House Plan - Elkhorn E.2

Welcome to Seaside Cottages in Birch Bay. This active AIR BNB is beautifully located with Terrill Creek out back and partial BAY VIEWS in front. This cozy cottage can be your home for full-time living or, a home away from home for the weekend getaway. It is quaint and perfect for relaxing. Low maintenance makes this home move-in ready. The cottage features two bedrooms, an upstairs loft, a full bath, laminate, and tile flooring, a woodburning fireplace, a covered front porch with composite decking, and a back deck to view all the creek has to offer. The open floor plan is ideal with natural light and vaulted ceilings. The location is highly desirable and close to all Birch Bay amenities. Public BEACH ACCESS is right across the street.

Discover the Glacier charm with this classic log cabin nestled beside the tranquil Nooksack River. Situated in a highly desirable location within the Mt Baker Rim, this pristine cabin offers peace, privacy, and a wealth of community amenities including a clubhouse, tennis courts, and a heated outdoor pool. This single-owner cabin boasts a timeless custom-built fireplace, a 50-year snaplock roof, a ductless heating/cooling system, two well-appointed bedrooms, and a charming loft. The large south-facing bay windows flood the living space with natural light and offer seamless views of the surrounding landscape. The cabin's prime location is just steps from the river ensuring days and nights filled with the soothing sounds of cascading water.

Beautiful 2, 400 square foot custom built home, situated on a quiet and non through street in the desirable Skyview neighborhood close to schools and parks. This home, only 10 minutes from Bellingham features an open floor plan, gourmet kitchen with pantry, half bath, and the primary bedroom with spacious ensuite on the main floor. Upper floor features a flex room, 2 bedrooms, full bath, and a large bonus room. Beautiful flooring creates a perfect contrast to the light filled great room, accented by a vaulted ceiling and a floor to ceiling rock fireplace. Large fully fenced backyard with a fun play structure and a covered deck that makes for perfect outdoor living and dining all year. THE PERFECT PLACE TO CALL HOME!

Welcome to your dream rambler-style home, where modern updates meet classic charm. Enjoy a FULLY REMODELED interior, a spacious open floor plan and a new kitchen boasting beautiful countertops and stainless steel appliances. Complete with brand new flooring and updated bathrooms. Nestled in a friendly neighborhood, this gem backs up to a large park, featuring a basketball court and playground. There are two inviting living rooms, perfect for cozy evenings by the fireplace and relaxing. Three bright bedrooms including a full primary suite with an oversized walk-in tile shower. The backyard with a patio is ideal for gatherings and play, with steps up leading to the park. Dont miss this perfect blend of style and comfort!

Classic Point Roberts cottage on private road, steps away from the golf course and the beach. This two bedroom cabin has received many updates and is ready for your summer gatherings. BRAND NEW Glendon Biofilter septic system, upgraded 200 amp electrical service panel and new wrap-around deck. The property has legal access to a staircase which leads to the entire, and rarely used, west facing seashore/beach. Additional 200 sq ft bunkhouse/storage building which can accommodate overflow guests. Extremely quiet neighborhood on the west side. This versatile property is ready for your personal touches. Landscaping seller credit available!

Welcome to the Whispering Meadows. This stunning single-level home has it all. The modern kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a huge quartz island, and soft-close cabinets. The spacious master suite boasts a double vanity in the bathroom and a large walk-in closet. Enjoy the convenience of a huge utility room. Generously sized office for those that work from home. The oversized 2-car garage provides ample storage space. Relax on the huge covered back patio overlooking your backyard. Each bedroom is equipped with mini splits to keep you cool in the summer and warm in the winter. Schedule your visit today and experience it for yourself!

Welcome to 1204 Haystack Ln! This gorgeous home boasts nearly 2, 600 SF, 3 beds, and 2.5 baths. As you walk inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors and an amazing corner office. The kitchen features stunning custom cabinets, high-end appliances, and a walk-in pantry. The vaulted ceiling in the living room offers a view of the covered patio with built-in heaters.The primary suite is truly amazing, featuring a large shower, walk-in closets, and heated floors. Upstairs, you'll find 2 more bedrooms, a full bath, and a large bonus room. This stunning home sits on over 1.5 acres of land with views of the foothills and plenty of room for a shop/outbuildings or potential future development.

Incredibly great price for an updated 3BR/1BA Craftsman in the York neighborhood! It's main feature is everything has been updated. An open kitchen, cozy sunroom perfect for an office or retreat, and a attic brimming with potential. New double-paned windows, Hardie-Plank siding, and newer roof w/ gutters provide long-lasting comfort. The home also offers updated plumbing, electrical, LED lighting with dimmer switches, fresh paint, and professionally refinished Fir floors. Stylish kitchen cabinets and modern appliances make cooking a delight. With off-alley parking that accommodates 4-5 vehicles plus a spacious backyard, and proximity to parks, downtown, and WWU, this home has it all, including the potential of building an ADU off the alley!

Rare opportunity - $10, 000 BUYER BONUS toward Buyer's closing cost and/or prepaids, or use to discount purchase price. Sunny and bright PNW contemporary home offers 3BR/1.75 baths. The home has been completely remodeled with new flooring, windows, fixtures, appliances, kitchen cabinets, butcher block countertops, updated electrical, new composite deck, new railing and staircase with metal grate steps. The upper level offers 900sq/ft of open living space with vaulted ceiling, French door, 2 generous sized bedrooms, 1 full bath including W/D and a huge sun deck with southwest exposure. The lower bonus room is accessed by separate exterior entrance with 1BR & 3/4BA plus large private deck. Enjoy all of the amenities in beautiful Sudden Valley.

Discover serene living on this expansive 4.82-acre property, just a short 10-minute drive from Barkley Village and the amenities of Bellingham. This spacious single-story home encompasses 1, 751 square feet and features 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms, and two living rooms. The interior is refreshed with new paint, modern vinyl plank flooring, and a recently updated roof. Enjoy the tranquility of your surroundings from the back deck, perfect for morning coffee or entertaining, framed by flourishing fruit trees and a generous backyard. The property also includes a versatile 2-bay shop ideal for parking, storage, or pursuing hobbies, alongside two spacious garden sheds. Convenient access to Mt. Baker Hwy for quick trips into Bellingham.

Motivated sellers listing this Custom newly built craftsman home. Just 25 miles from Mt Baker Ski Area and at the base of Red Mountain on 1.23 level acres. Upper living quarters showcase vaulted ceilings with pine T&G, knotty alder solid doors and trim, butcher block countertops, propane fireplace, heat pump, walk in closet & soft close cabinetry. Downstairs has a bedroom with closet and 1/2 bath. Fully insulated & drywalled 40x17 shop w/18 ceiling has 6 concrete & wired for a vehicle lift. Smaller 22x17 garage also insulated & drywalled. Fiber optic internet installed along with custom security system. Brand new 3 bedroom septic system. 12x16 & 10x12 sheds allow for extra storage. Dog kennel w/dog door w/ access to inside on back of home.

Discover the charm and meticulous craftsmanship of 2925 Sumerset in the coveted Glenhaven Lakes Community. Rebuilt in 1997 with a keen eye for detail, this home features a completely cedar-clad interior that creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The greatroom, with its soaring vaulted ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows, frames breathtaking views of your own enchanted forest. Enjoy the comfort of a cozy wood-burning fireplace, unwind in the sauna, or take in the serene surroundings from the open loft that overlooks the greatroom. Entertain in the spacious bonus room, wrap-around deck or patio! The circular driveway ensures abundant parking and there's covered storage for all your outdoor gear- welcome to your adventure base camp.

This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with over half an acre of land is a must see! With over half an acre of beautifully landscaped land, this immaculate residence is designed to provide a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and functionality. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by an open-concept floor plan that maximizes natural light and enhances the sense of space. The main living area features large windows, and premium laminate flooring, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The living room is perfect for relaxing or entertaining, with a cozy fireplace serving as the focal point. The oversized 2 car garage is perfect for your hobbies. This home is literally move in ready. Lots of options with this property. It won't last long at this price!

Wonderful layout in a fantastic location in a quiet neighborhood. Walk into this bright, open-concept home filled with natural light. Living room & kitchen transition perfectly, leading to a covered outdoor patio that backs up to green space, expanding the privacy & open feel of the property. Kitchen features quartz counters, upgraded appliances and bar ideal for entertaining. Relax next to the gas fireplace with a tile accents in the living room, boasting view windows & vaulted ceilings. Primary bedroom is spacious with a beautifully appointed bath featuring a tile shower, ample storage & generous walk-in closet. Bonus room adds flexibility to great plan. Dont miss this opportunity to own a home that combines comfort, style, & convenience

Your architecturally-unique 1 bedroom condo awaits! The custom cantilevered staircase, vaulted ceilings, & open floor plan give this space an airy & artistic feel while the large deck sets it apart from others in the complex. No rental cap or restrictions making the opportunity endless. Enjoy the cozy gas fireplace, in-unit washer/dryer, and XL windows for plenty of natural light & views of gorgeous foliage make this home one you have to see! Walking distance to restaurants, 18-hole championship golf course, Lake Whatcom beaches, community pools, trails and so much more!

Lovely Rambler on a nice level lot nestled in the Mount Baker Foothills. Open floor plan accented by laminate floors and tons of natural light through the large windows. Super efficient Heat Pump keeps you cool in the summer and cozy in the winter. primary suite enjoys the mountain views via the sliding glass doors that lead to the backyard patio and has a full bath and walk in closet. High Speed internet available for work at home option. Home is wired for a generator. Easy 30 minute commute to Bellingham and close to all of the activities the Mount Baker Recreation area has to offer!

Experience tranquility in this tastefully updated top-floor, 2 bed, end-unit condo, offering the best location in the community! Nestled between the 3rd Green fountain & 4th Tee of the Bellingham Golf & CC, this sanctuary boasts two private balconies, perfect for relaxing in peace. Inside you will enjoy a remodeled kitchen featuring modern finishes, as well as fresh paint and new flooring throughout. The primary bedroom is a true haven with a huge walk-in closet & en-suite bathroom w/tub. Cozy up by the gas fireplace in the inviting living area designed for comfort and natural light. With its serene vibes, thoughtful updates & privacy, its the ultimate location to call home, and feel like you have the whole place to yourself!

Nestled on a tranquil dead-end street in the coveted Alabama Hill neighborhood, this home sits on a generous lot adjacent to city property to the north. Beautifully renovated in 2023 with new kitchen, baths, roof, Hardy siding, updated systems and fixtures, it blends modern amenities into open-concept living areas. The lower level's expansive Rec room is versatile (game room, screening room, gym). Step into the Chef's kitchen where the windows and light offer a view of the surrounding landscape. The tiered lot finishes below to a slab that is large enough for a regulation pickleball court. Turnkey ready for discerning buyers seeking modern comfort in a serene neighborhood setting.

Rare opportunity to purchase a charming fixer in beautiful Sunnyland, built in 1924! Perfect for first-time home buyers or investors looking for a blank canvas to activate your creative side and transform this property to its full potential. This gem boasts a fantastic location - just a stroll away from Trader Joes and the delightful Sunnyland shops, and a quick drive or bike ride to Downtown Bellingham, Sunset or Barkley Village. The front porch has been redone and the bathroom received a a modern upgrade in 2014 with a new shower and sheetrock. As you approach the front door trees bloom gracefully over the arching walkway, welcoming you home in style! 2 Outbuildings for all your storage needs.

Great opportunity to become a homeowner in Sandy Point Heights! Spacious, updated, three bedroom, two bath home on a spacious corner lot with a wrap around driveway and private backyard. Enter to the open living space with adjacent dining area. Kitchen features bar eating/sitting space, freshly painted cabinets, pantry space, and brand new dishwasher. Hallway leads to all three bedrooms. Primary bedroom at end of hallway offers en suite primary bathroom. Back yard offers covered deck space, large grass area, storage shed, and a tree house!

Welcome to River-Walk, a unique NW Washington community offering attractive design, luxurious finishes, beautiful views & pedestrian-friendly connectivity to Lynden. Walk or bike a few blocks to downtown to Lyndens quaint restaurants & stores. River-Walk is less than two hours to Seattle, Vancouver, B.C., Mt. Baker & the San Juan Islands. Lot 14 is in River-Walks west side, reserved for 55-and-older active adults with tech features including high-speed fiber optic cable. It offers a comfortable 1864 sqft with 3 bedrooms & 2.25 bathrooms. The gourmet kitchen is highlighted by quartz countertops & islands with full waterfall drops. Direct GPS to 202 Riverview Road, Lynden.

MOVE-IN READY! Contemporary and eco-friendly with UPGRADES. NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes end unit features, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. This unique end unit has upgrades; ceiling fans in both bedrooms, tub/shower in upstairs bath, LVP throughout including stairs + bedrooms. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Showings available between 12-3pm, 7dys a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

Near I-5, in the path of progress new larger round-a-bouts coming for increased traffic flow (maybe the next West Bakerview??). The shop is 32x48' w/RV height doors 3/4 bath. It also has adjoining 18x40' RV carport. The house, 972' w/unfinished 972' basement and an unfinished large attic. Updated Electrical and plumbing and natural gas. Numerous sheds, carports and lean-tos. House has water from local water association, and the property also has a well. Attached carport to the house, and a single unattached garage. Mount Baker view!

NEW PRICE! NEW PRICE! Water View Penthouse on the Semiahmoo Sandspit! Spacious design w/ large great room & truly gourmet kitchen w/ top of the line appliances: Wolfe range, Sub-Zero fridge, granite countertops & loads of custom cabinetry. The Primary suite is spa like. Private guest quarters, efficient den plus a floating loft. The covered deck off the living room completes this truly outstanding home. Two assigned underground parking spaces w/ large adjacent walled-in storeroom. Your membership allows you to Enjoy all that the Resort at Semiahmoo has to offer: Arnold Palmer golf course, Inn at Semiahmoo w/ pool & health club. Take the time out to walk the miles of beach/walking trails. IT, S MORE THAN A COMMUNITY, IT, S A LIFE=STYLE!!

Bucket-list property!!! Everyone knows someone who wants acreage to build on. This 10 acre piece of level land is approx. 50% treed and partially fenced. There's open space to the north, south and west that will provide even a more private feeling. The views of Mt. Baker, Mt. Shuksan and the Canadian Coast range are a cherry on top for those looking for acreage to call home. Several hundred plants and trees have recently been planted on the property and are just taking root. This location is ideally located in central Whatcom County. Wetland study just completed. Seller completed a perk test for a septic system and water shares are available through the Custer Water Association, per the association.

Own a piece of Glacier history, it's been 20 years since this little rustic GEM has been on the market. Located in the sought after Snowline Community! This 2 bedrooms with smaller flex room, is ready for your personal touches! Large beautiful deck to enjoy the outdoors! Some of the amenities include gated entry, outdoor pool, tennis courts, fishing pond, playground, walking trails, community clubhouse & for year round recreation. Currently a part time vacation rental, the opportunity exists to continue using the home as an income earning property. Your own cozy place to make memories! 20 mins to Mt. Baker, and 15 to Silver Lake!

Contemporary home in The Meadows Development. 3 Bedrooms 2 bathrooms with a large office & Laundry. The kitchen has modern soft close cabinets, Stainless steel appliances quartz counters, a Tiled backsplash, and a large breakfast bar. The primary suite has a beautiful walk-in tiled shower with a bench and rain shower head. walk-in custom closet with built-in cabinets. Speakers in the ceilings, A/C, electrostatic filter for your air, front deck to enjoy your view. 2 entrances to this home, you can park on Brian ct in your garage and walk up the stairs to your home or park on Rossie ln and walk into your home. Home is a zero-lot line. Walking distance to Elementary and Middle School. Walking trails in the Meadows and a tree-lined boulevard.

Welcome to the Whispering Meadows. Experience single level living at its finest in this 3 bed 2.5 bath home. The living area features soaring high ceilings and a stunning floor-to-ceiling shiplap gas fireplace. The kitchen is a culinary dream with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a large kitchen island, and soft-close cabinets. The master suite offers a stand-alone soaker tub, a walk-in shower, and an oversized walk-in closet. Each bedroom is equipped with mini splits to keep you cool in the summer and warm in the winter. Oversized utility room with a built in bench seat. Enjoy the convenience of a spacious 3-car garage. Nice covered back patio overlooking your spacious backyard. This home truly has it all.

Meticulously maintained Victorian residence in the Lettered Streets invites you to step into a world of timeless allure and original character. Extensive Fir floors and Millwork exude the charm of yesteryear. Modern kitchen with an eating nook, perfect setting for culinary delights. Entertain with a formal dining room. Light-filled rooms with tall windows, create a welcoming ambiance. Main floor den with French doors and a full bath features a clawfoot tub. Laundry room with a wash sink. Upstairs, 3 spacious bedrooms and a bath. Easy access to the waterfront activities with a marina nearby for leisurely strolls or nautical adventures. Fenced, private backyard with patio. Newer garage with alley access. A captivating haven awaiting.

Immaculate, like-new home in the private lake access community of Agate Bay Estates. Astounding yard space complete with 2 porches, 2 cedar sheds, pergola, and space for entertaining. Lake Whatcom beach rights and dock space only minutes away. The primary suite complete w/ WIC and full bath, while the home offers 2 additional bedrooms and second full bath. All new appliances, flooring, lighting, and carport. Can be a second home or year 'round. Space lease includes covers water/sewer, garbage. All ages park, no rentals, no dogs, with 25 homes.

Must see this serene and inviting home! Extensively updated in 2024, this stunning Skeers home backs onto Galbraith Mountains bike trails and features thoughtful interior design notes with quality materials. Short walk to Whatcom Falls Park! Features a 2024 roof, new solid cherry hardwood floors, a new kitchen, and more. Open kitchen/living plan perfect for entertaining. The spacious primary bedroom is on the main level with a private bath, free tub, dual shower, walk-in closet. Upstairs, find two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and an open loft area perfect for an office, music room, or home workspace. The private, beautifully landscaped backyard has no homes behind it. Modern home, surrounded by nature, close to town. Unmissable!

Single level condo with garage sits on the 5th green, enjoy the outdoor beauty of this unique end unit with views of the golf course, ponds, Mt. Baker/surrounding mountains, and sunrises. Vaulted ceilings w/picture windows flood the living space with natural light. This 2 bed 2 bath home has air-conditioning for complete comfort, beautiful gas fireplace, master bath has a jetted tub w/separate walk-in shower. Nice attached garage for easy parking and storage. Brand new luxury vinyl plank in LV room, dining, hallway, kitchen, and guest bath as well brand new carpet in both bedrooms. Sit on the deck or spread out to the adjacent grassy green space! Close to everything, this is easy living at its finest!

The Sunnyland charmer you've been waiting for! This light & bright single level craftsman has been tastefully updated and could not be more perfect! Centrally located and walking distance to your favorite restaurants, breweries, Trader Joes & more! Just wait until you see this primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings & en-suite bathroom. New hardwood floors, paint, counters & more make this home move in ready. The fully fenced, full sun yard is low maintenance but has mature fruit trees, garden beds and even a chicken coop! 2 small storage spaces for all your tools & toys. Property has received amazing short term rental income that could continue or be used as your next home!

Brand new home located on a double lot, with massive garage! This home has 9 foot ceilings throughout the main level, and a large deck on the rear of the home. There is also a landscaped firepit area behind the home! Features include: Open kitchen with stainless appliances, white cabinet package, & oversized island for casual dining & entertainment. Luxury vinyl plank flooring with gas fireplace as the centerpiece in the great room. Primary suite with 5 piece ensuite bath & large walk-in closet. Family room, full bath, additional laundry, & 4th bedroom down (or private suite - w/exterior entrance potential). Large garage w/storage room (or potentially a wine cellar!). Loads of 'elbow room' here with the 2 lots! Wonderful neighborhood.

Located in the desirable Tweed Twenty Neighborhood, this single-level home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on a spacious lot. The house awaits your personal touch, perfect for those looking for a project with cosmetic updates. The kitchen boasts newer appliances and is open to the living room. A large family room features a gas fireplace. Major updates in 2008 include a new roof, vinyl siding, and windows. The large fenced backyard is easy to maintain. Conveniently close to schools, shopping, trails, parks, and Lake Whatcom. This as-is renovation opportunity is attractively priced and has great potential.

Pride of ownership is evident in this impeccable home at the Reserve at Cordata. Lovely two story, three bedrooms with primary bedroom on main level, two car garage, low maintenance front yard. New furnace and air conditioner, washer, dryer, microwave, carpet, new floor in utility room Solar energy for greatly reduced monthly PSE bills. Home backs up to lush greenbelt for privacy while sitting on the deck in the fully fenced back yard. Storage building in back yard and gas plumbed at the outdoor patio. Ready for you to move in!

The perfect condo for full-time or part-time living. Here is your chance to own a condo in one of the best condo complexes in Birch Bay. Enjoy a short walk to the beach, or walk across the street to enjoy the pool (seasonal) and large party room. Well-kept condo that backs to greenbelt for privacy. Updated with new carpet and paint. Good size primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings and reading nook. Second bedroom and bathroom upstairs with half bath downstairs. Kitchen with eat-in area and slider to the private deck. Furniture is negotiable, so all you have to do is bring your personal items and move in! This condo is ideal for first-time home buyers, snowbirds or anyone seeking an ideal second home.

Discover your dream home in Woodbine Estates! This impeccably maintained single-level home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and an office, providing ample space for work and relaxation. Enjoy the seamless layout connecting the living room, kitchen, dining, and family room, perfect for entertaining. The updated kitchen boasts custom cabinets, SS appliances, granite countertops, gas range, eating bar, and under-cabinet lighting. Relax by the cozy fireplace, adding warmth and charm to the living space. This move-in-ready, low-maintenance home features fresh interior paint, a recently painted exterior, and a newer roof. Mature landscaping ensures privacy, while the location just outside city limits provides easy access to Lakeway and Lake Padden.

2.99% assumable loan for VA buyers! Timeless and thoughtful, this single-level home in an established Lynden neighborhood is designed for both comfort & luxury. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with sitting area, deluxe walk-in closet, heated marble floors, jetted tub, & bath side fireplace. Every detail has been considered in the many updates throughout. Exposed beams & craftsman touches add classic style, while skylights & solar tubes give this home a light, bright feel. Entertaining is easy with open kitchen, two living spaces, and vinyl plank flooring throughout. Enjoy the mature landscape in the large, fenced backyard from the deck, or retreat indoors to the A/C. Home backs to a park and is wired for generator. Perfection!

One of the largest homes in the neighborhood + Single level living & a 5min walk to the beach - All in the Cottonwood Beach neighborhood! This home is 2, 474sqft w/3 bed, 3.25 bath & office w/built in desks. Chefs kitchen w/prep room, walk-in pantry & lots of storage space! Open concept living & dining w/separate family room. Primary suite has large walk-in closet & 5 piece bath. On the opposite end of the home are 2 baths, 2 beds & the office. Newer paint throughout. Great patio space out front-perfect place to enjoy those warm summer nights! New 30 year roof installed in November. Lots of parking available-enough for an RV. Close to town, walking trails, parks, golfing and more. Great summer home or investment property. Welcome home!

Welcome to Crossridge Urban Community! Brand new single family homes that have been thoughtfully designed with architectural & community integrity, each home feels custom with its elevated finishes and interior design. The Arroyo model has all the living on main floor that extends out through modern French doors onto a large covered patio.
